    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Safety Equipment - Required</title>
        <para>Fire Extinguisher removal and check.</para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">The fire extinguisher is generally mounted in the area around the driver position (
                <hotlnk document="s47005_13.xml" xrefid="f4700549">Fig. 49, Item 4</hotlnk>). Locate the extinguisher
                and mounting bracket.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Release the strap latch securing the extinguisher to the base mounting bracket.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Locate the bracket mounting screws, loosen and remove.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the extinguisher mounting bracket.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">With extinguisher bracket removed, secure the extinguisher in the bracket assembly and latch
                the locking strap. This is to prevent any damage to the extinguisher or the possibility of the
                extinguisher being discharged.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f47005177" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g47005177.webp" filename="../figg47/g47005177.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="248px"/>
            <caption>Figure 177. First Aid Kit Mounting Bracket</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">FIRST AID KIT UPPER MOUNTING SCREWS</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">FIRST AID KIT LOWER MOUNTING BRACKET</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">INTERIOR FRONT HEADER PANEL ASSEMBLY</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <para>First Aid Kit</para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">The first aid kid is generally mounted on the front bulkhead over the windshield assembly (
                <hotlnk document="s47005_32.xml" xrefid="f4700590">Fig. 90, Item 2</hotlnk>). The first aid kit is
                secured in a mounting bracket to the bulkhead structure.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Release the lower clip on the mounting bracket, loosen and remove the first aid kit mounting
                screw at the top of the handle assembly.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the first aid kit.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcsubproc>
